hoose the tennis option.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 644, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Now we want to show you the shooting.\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can watch the tennis on BBC1' I come out, channels, BBC1.\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 712, \"end\": 716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9902951944407055, \"rank\": 0.00979991179758565, \"text\": \"BBC1\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tennis.\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 753, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"5 minutes later 'We are now going to the gymnastics, you can watch the tennis on the app' WTAF [crying laughing emoji]\\\".\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 876, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another social media user added: \\\"@DawnLoweActress @BBCSport @DjokerNole Typical BBC - and then you have 3 bbc commentators commentating on the same piece of apparatus at the gymnastics and someone in the studio endlessly discussing the same thing - and I am paying for it - Grrrrrrr !\\\"\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9915390621180294, \"rank\": 0.008486672077394654, \"text\": \"bbc\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Team GB Olympian cries live on BBC and apologises for devastating failure    Someone else seemed to be annoyed about missing out on particular sports, writing: \\\"When there is gymnastics and climbing going on bbc are showing badminton and table tennis\\\", with another adding: \\\"BBCneeds to get it together.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"h